How to Run

Run Backend:

bash

cd backend
docker build -t jobverifier-backend .
docker run -p 5000:5000 jobverifier-backend


Run Frontend:

bash

python frontend/main.py

Run Everything with Docker Compose:

bash

chmod +x build.sh
./build.sh

docker-compose ps


Check if EXE was created

docker exec -it jobverifier-frontend bash
ls /app/dist/

ex: main.exe


copy 
docker cp jobverifier-frontend:/app/dist/main.exe .

run
./main.exe
